Text.string: Hey, hey you! Yes, you! Whoever's listening to this! I'm in a bind, okay?! I need these Dynasty Burgers delivered to people in the area! And I mean RIGHT AWAY! Go on! Do it!
And if you see any of my competitor's signs, shoot 'em down and I'll give you some extra time!
Whenever you're around and need work, come talk to this sign spinner. People ALWAYS want burgers, my dude!
Ready to deliver some more burgers and fulfill your lifelong dream of being a delivery driver?! Nice! Let's do it!
Delivery time! People are hungry for burgers, my dude! Get them the burgers!
Come on! Come on! These burgers aren't gonna deliver themselves! Although... that would be amazing!
And take down those Legacy Drive-Thru signs for bonus time, my dude!
Definitely wreck those Legacy signs if you see them. I'll cut you some slack on time if you do!
You gotta take out my competition's signs, too! I'll give you bonus time for it!
Woooo! You deliver burgers like it's your freakin' job! Which it technically was for a little while there, but still. Woooo! Extra big payment for you!
That was pretty good, Vault Hunter. You might have a future in this game if you play your cards right.
I've seen better, but I've seen worse.
Head back to my sign spinner for your pay, yeah?
Remember not to directly address the sign spinner. They've got a job to do. Anyway! You did good, my dude! Thanks for your help! Come back for more any time!
Do not speak directly to the sign spinner. They're busy. But YOU?! My dude! You did good work today! Come back again any time!
Oh, yeah. That sign spinner is actually mute. But hey! You got those burgers delivered! Nice! Come back any time!
Yeah! Screw you, Legacy Drive-Thru!
Hnngh! Takin' down the competition!
Bonus time!
Ooh! Nice shot!
Ha! Take that, Legacy!
Yes! Great shot!
Holy crap! You got those delivered SO FAST! Where have you been all my life, my dream delivery driver?! I'm gonna give you an extra big tip for doing such a great job! AWESOME!
Oh man, you're the best! Those burgers were gettin' cold, and there's NOTHING more tragic than cold freakin' burgers! Thank you!
That's one juicy burger! Delivered hot and fresh! Ish.
Enjoy your burger, whoever you are!
Remember: Dynasty Diner means quality burgers!
Great delivery! You make me proud to call you my temporary employee!
Burger delivery! Eat up before it gets cold!
Nom down that burger, beloved customer dude!
I thought you were faster than this!
Time's tickin' down! Better hurry!
Check the time, my dude! Move! Move!
You'll have to move faster than that!
Faster! Faster, I say!
Don't let the burgers get cold, my dude!
Well, I mean... I've seen faster drivers. But I'll say this for you: you did it! Eventually! Thanks!
Head on back to the sign spinner for your payment, okay?
